@startuml
' Diagram: F09 - Giam sat khach dang online va xem hanh trinh live (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, HEAD 6510344
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/BanDo/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/BanDo/Index.cshtml: loadData(), showHistory()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/HeartbeatController.cs: GetActive(), GetHistory()
' Note: Sequence da duoc kiem tra tu endpoint den JS renderer; co the dung cho bao cao neu module BanDo khong doi them.
title F09 - Giam sat khach dang online va xem hanh trinh live

actor Admin
participant "BanDo IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant "BanDo JS + Leaflet" as JS
participant "HeartbeatController" as HeartbeatController
participant AppDbContext
database DB

Admin -> IndexModel: mo /BanDo
IndexModel -> AppDbContext: load POI dang hoat dong
AppDbContext -> DB: SELECT poi(trangthai=true)
DB --> AppDbContext: pois
IndexModel --> JS: page + API_BASE + PoisJson
JS -> JS: khoi tao Leaflet map + ve marker POI

loop moi 30 giay
  JS -> HeartbeatController: GET /api/heartbeat/active
  HeartbeatController -> DB: query VitriKhach online + LichSuPhat + DangKyApp
  DB --> HeartbeatController: items
  HeartbeatController --> JS: { count, items }
  JS -> JS: guestLayer.clearLayers()\nrenderDeviceList(items)
end

opt admin xem lich su mot thiet bi
  Admin -> JS: click "Xem hanh trinh"
  JS -> HeartbeatController: GET /api/heartbeat/history/{deviceShort}
  HeartbeatController -> DB: tim MaThietBi + join LichSuPhat voi POI
  DB --> HeartbeatController: lich su
  HeartbeatController --> JS: { soDiemDaGhe, lichSu[] }
  JS --> Admin: modal lich su + link Google Maps
end
@enduml
